   Command Note     lp print with good defaults   lpc status all See printer settings   lprm clear print jobs   export PRINTER='Sharp-MX-2700N&rsquo; Set the target printer before printing   lpoptions See available options    I generally print PDFs, using the excellent pdf-tools. This provides C-c C-p which will print with the $PRINTER and settings you&rsquo;ve configured, but sometimes you need more customization.